title: 5 Real Horror Stories That Inspired 'American Horror Story'
author: Top5s
comment: Twisty definitely wasn't the scariest character. His backstory made him less scary.
My obsession for serial killers is getting unhealthy. I knew about every story mentioned in this video.
damn i think im the only person that isn't afraid of clowns.
I liked Twisty, his story was very heart breaking '-' all what he wanted was making kids smile.
had to Google cute kitten pictures after this. I'm a real man.
